Yes and yes. Users range from Information Professionals to "naive" end
users.
If there's a string like "N-(t-Butyl)-N-(3,5-dinitrobenzoyl)-nitroxyl" =
users
can be expected to search for "dinitro", "3,5-dinitro", "nitrobenz" =
