> -----Original Message-----
> From: Ben Litchfield [mailto:ben@csh.rit.edu]
> Sent: Tuesday, November 25, 2003 9:45 AM
> To: Lucene Users List
> Subject: RE: Lucene refresh index function (incremental indexing).
